// 11 - DeveloperSecurity: Any Developer Security tool such as an Infrastrucre-as-Securty (IAC) scanner, Secrets Detection, or Secure Software Development Lifecycle (SSDLC) tool that can detect sensitive data and/or enforce data security policies. E.g., TruffleHog, GitGuardian, Git-Secrets.
